name: Meta AI
summary: Meta, the parent company of Facebook and Instagram, is making significant advancements in artificial intelligence (AI) with the release of Llama 3, its large language model. Meta AI is now being integrated across Meta's platforms, including Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp, and Messenger. One notable development is the addition of real-time AI image generation to WhatsApp. Meta's latest AI chatbot, built on the Llama 3 foundation, is being introduced. This new AI model is designed to be less "sanctimonious" and more user-friendly. The ongoing rivalry between tech giants like Meta, OpenAI, and Google is fueling these AI advancements. Meta's expansion into AI poses potential concerns about the spread of misinformation on its platforms. Despite these concerns, Meta's AI initiatives aim to enhance user experiences and expand AI capabilities across its products.
